Invocation Name: smooth eddie
des:
Smooth Eddie is the smoothest coolest greased up player that walks the strip. If he says something to you, feel privileged for being so lucky.

Speaking of lucky, you are in fact SO lucky that you get to hear Smooth Eddie's awesomeness on your Alexa product.

Just say: "Alexa, ask Smooth Eddie" and feel the grease just ooooze out of him.

If this app made you fall in love with Smooth Eddie, there is more where that came from. Call me.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
